= Introduction =

{{project_name}} has an iptables rules script and firewall configuration file for both {{gateway_product_name}} and {{workstation_product_name}}. {{gateway_product_name}} firewall features include: <ref>https://github.com/{{project_name_short}}/whonix-firewall</ref>
<div style="column-count:2;-moz-column-count:2;-webkit-column-count:2">
* transparent proxying
* stream isolation
* reject invalid packages
* fail closed mechanism
* optional VPN-Firewall
* optional isolating proxy
* optional incoming flash proxy
* optional Tor relay
</div>
The firewall should not be removed unless you no longer wish to use {{project_name}}.

